title: Fantastic Executive house in Moraga, 4 bedrooms, 3 baths
posting_body: ['Fantastic Executive house in Moraga, 4 bedrooms, 3 baths', '-The elegant house locates in a prestigious private area with open mountain view and end of cul-de-sac.', 'Easy access to freeway and Bart station (about 15 minutes)', '-Master suite has large walk-in closets and Jacuzzi bath tub', '- Kitchen has spacious open space, Granite Counters and Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Three beautiful Fireplaces in the house', '- Living, dinning and family rooms have beautiful hardwood flooring and vaulted ceilings', '- Big Backyard , a wonderful spa, a huge deck with astonishing view', '-Washer and dryer hookups', '-Central air conditioning and heating', '- Large 3 car garage', '-Gardener and home warranty are paid by owner.', '-Rent $6300/month.', '12-Months or longer Lease and Security Deposit (equals one month rent)', '-Pets O.K', '-Available 09/15/2022', 'Please text', 'show contact info', 'or e-mail']
